			<div class="content" id="post-content-4427656">
									

<p>A joke article regarding image use both in- and out-of-universe. Thanks goes to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sooperrandomname" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2752472); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2752472&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1576156186" alt="Sooperrandomname" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2752472)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sooperrandomname" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2752472); return false;">Sooperrandomname</a></span> for critiquing, and a few randos on the SCP Unity Discord for supporting the idea.</p>
<p>I'd also like to thank <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rokurokubi" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5700026); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5700026&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1576156186" alt="Rokurokubi" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5700026)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rokurokubi" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5700026); return false;">Rokurokubi</a></span>, who not only is writing a Japanese translation of this article, but managed to extract the necessary forum formatting from <a href="/scp-3309">SCP-3309</a>, as well as spotting numerous tiny formatting errors which had slipped into the final article.</p>
<p><em>Most</em> images (See reply by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/c-dives" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2375337); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2375337&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1576156186" alt="C-Dives" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2375337)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/c-dives" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2375337); return false;">C-Dives</a></span>) used in the article itself are in the public domain. Exact sources can be found below:</p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;show&nbsp;block</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">–&nbsp;hide&nbsp;block</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>Image of Locus-248-J<br />
<a href="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/1/19/Pub%2C_Interior.jpg/337px-Pub%2C_Interior.jpg">https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/1/19/Pub%2C_Interior.jpg/337px-Pub%2C_Interior.jpg</a></p>
<p>Image of a California Bald-necked Chicken<br />
<a href="https://www.needpix.com/photo/422722/brown-hen-bald-necked-chicken">https://www.needpix.com/photo/422722/brown-hen-bald-necked-chicken</a></p>
<p>Portion of The Garden of Earthly Delights<br />
<a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Hieronymus_Bosch_-_The_Garden_of_Earthly_Delights_-_Hell.jpg">https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Hieronymus_Bosch_-_The_Garden_of_Earthly_Delights_-_Hell.jpg</a></p>
<p>Image of a chicken (used in &quot;Photoshopped&quot; image)<br />
<a href="https://www.publicdomainpictures.net/en/view-image.php?image=263414&amp;picture=golden-wyandotte-chicken-2">https://www.publicdomainpictures.net/en/view-image.php?image=263414&amp;picture=golden-wyandotte-chicken-2</a></p>
<p>Image of a can of Budweiser (used in &quot;Photoshopped&quot; image)<br />
<a href="http://www.peakpx.com/442719/red-gold-and-red-budweiser-can">http://www.peakpx.com/442719/red-gold-and-red-budweiser-can</a></p>
<p>Image of a cigarette (used in &quot;Photoshopped&quot; image)<br />
<a href="https://www.publicdomainpictures.net/en/view-image.php?image=38023&amp;picture=cigarette">https://www.publicdomainpictures.net/en/view-image.php?image=38023&amp;picture=cigarette</a></p>
<p>Image of a bottle cap (used in &quot;Photoshopped&quot; image)<br />
<a href="https://www.pexels.com/photo/alcohol-beer-bottle-cap-bottle-top-2708317/">https://www.pexels.com/photo/alcohol-beer-bottle-cap-bottle-top-2708317/</a></p>
<p>The &quot;Missing image&quot; from the final collapsible is taken from <a href="/scp-231">SCP-231</a>.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p>The <a href="https://imgur.com/a/oBf7zuW">linked image</a> is, to my knowledge, not licenced under Creative Commons, and thus isn't displayed in the article itself.</p>

