			<div class="content" id="post-content-4427819">
									

<p>Ultimately, this is super well-written, gotta give you props there. That being said, the joke fell super flat for me. The set-up was entirely too long and it was completely non-sequitur to the actual punchline. Additionally, said punchline didn't strike me as absurd enough to justify the lack of pacing in the joke itself.</p>
<p>Ultimately, I have just one criterion that I judge a -J on, and this one didn't cut it. Sorry, but I didn't laugh. -1</p>
